Version 2.0

	* Compatible with TYPO3 8.7
	* Refactor code to use PHP namespaces
	* Add support for TCEMAIN.previewDomain
	* Fix: Do not rely on pages.url_scheme (field does not exist anymore)
	* Use Exceptions for error handling

